Barclays Cuts Asset Financing to Smaller Companies, Times Says

-- B y   J o h n   S i m p s o n
-- 
2011-02-14T01:24:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-14/barclays-cuts-asset-financing-to-smaller-companies-times-says.html
  Barclays Plc  has told customers with
revenue below 5 million pounds ($8 million) that it will no
longer provide them with asset financing, used to buy machinery,
office equipment or vehicles, the London-based Times reported,
citing the bank.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
